data.description: Welcome to this remodeled 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 2 car garage. The home was built in 1979 and remodeled in 2021. New central heating and air, granite countertops throughout, laminate flooring with Carpet in Bedrooms and ceiling fans. Exterior and interior new paint, light fixtures throughout and stainless steel appliances were replaced during remodel in 2021. Family room, features, brick, wood-burning fireplace, sliding glass door leads to covered back patio with large backyard and additional concrete on side of house. Home is located near schools, park and shopping centers.
